Bisa melihat Chen berkeluarga…

245
00:15:48,600 --> 00:15:50,400
dan menikahi Adik Ipar sebaik dirimu,

246
00:15:50,960 --> 00:15:52,560
walau aku harus mati saat ini juga,

247
00:15:54,200 --> 00:15:55,720
aku tak punya penyesalan.

248
00:15:56,560 --> 00:15:57,680
- Kami…
- Kakak.

249
00:15:58,560 --> 00:16:00,240
Mengmeng sedang marah kepadaku.

250
00:16:00,360 --> 00:16:01,520
Aku bicara sebentar dengannya.

251
00:16:01,680 --> 00:16:02,520
Baik.

252
00:16:03,440 --> 00:16:04,480
Kemari.

253
00:16:06,480 --> 00:16:07,640
Murong Chen, mau apa?

254
00:16:08,640 --> 00:16:09,640
Kenapa tak membiarkanku
memberitahu kakakmu…

255
00:16:09,800 --> 00:16:11,080
kita telah membatalkan pernikahan?

256
00:16:11,240 --> 00:16:12,120
Kakakku saja sudah seperti itu,

257
00:16:12,240 --> 00:16:13,400
apa kau tidak bisa melihatnya?

258
00:16:18,560 --> 00:16:20,320
Jangan kekang aku dengan moralitas.

259
00:16:21,080 --> 00:16:22,680
Aku akui, dia sangat kasihan.

260
00:16:23,720 --> 00:16:24,840
Tapi aku tak bisa mengorbankan hidupku…

261
00:16:24,960 --> 00:16:26,200
karena dia kasihan.

262
00:16:26,400 --> 00:16:28,160
Aku tak memintamu
menemaniku seumur hidup.

263
00:16:28,680 --> 00:16:30,280
Jarang sekali kakakku bisa tersenyum.

264
00:16:30,560 --> 00:16:32,200
Aku hanya ingin membuat dia bahagia.

265
00:16:34,160 --> 00:16:34,960
Mengmeng.

266
00:16:35,080 --> 00:16:36,160
Anggap aku memohon padamu.

267
00:16:36,320 --> 00:16:38,160
Temani aku untuk
berakting dua hari lagi.

268
00:16:44,960 --> 00:16:45,960
Hanya dua hari lagi.

269
00:16:47,960 --> 00:16:49,080
Terima kasih, Mengmeng.

270
00:16:51,240 --> 00:16:52,040
Kakak.

271
00:16:52,920 --> 00:16:53,880
Di luar angin kencang,

272
00:16:54,080 --> 00:16:55,400
kuantar kembali
ke tempat peristirahatan dulu.

273
00:16:56,360 --> 00:16:57,520
Merepotkanmu.

274
00:16:57,720 --> 00:16:58,400
Mengmeng.

275
00:16:58,560 --> 00:17:00,520
Apa kita masih mau pergi?

276
00:17:01,120 --> 00:17:02,600
Kita ikut mereka dulu.

277
00:17:06,140 --> 00:17:08,280
(Stasiun)

278
00:17:41,760 --> 00:17:43,560
Kau sengaja menghalangi jalanku?

279
00:18:10,480 --> 00:18:11,480
Aku lapar sekali.

280
00:18:13,760 --> 00:18:15,000
Apa kau bisa sopan sedikit?

281
00:18:15,320 --> 00:18:17,200
Tuan rumah pun
belum menggerakkan sumpit.

282
00:18:21,560 --> 00:18:22,520
Tidak perlu sungkan,

283
